text: Jake Short (born on May 30, 1997) is an American actor. He is known for his roles in various television series and movies. Short is from Indiana. == Career == Short gained fame for his role as Nose in the movie Shorts,and for his role as Fletcher Quimby in the Disney Channel sitcom A.N.T. Farm which aired from 2011 to 2014. He also played Oliver in the Disney XD series Mighty Med from 2013 to 2015 and Lab Rats: Elite Force in 2016. == References == == Other websites == * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Indiana
